            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#SPS">
                <p>Sacred to Silvanus Augustus. In honour of Lucius Valerius Nymphodotus, sexvir and, by the decree of the decurions, Augustalis, and Gaius Statius Primigenius, and in memory of Gaius Status Heuretus, sexvir and, by the decree of the decurions, Augustalis. the freedman Alypus [set this up].</p>
